data.title: The Wolf Pack sustains operations around the clock
data.meta_description: With nearly 40 F-16 Fighting Falcons assigned to the 8th Operations Group’s 80th and 35th Fighter Squadrons, the Wolf Pack is capable of providing combat airpower round-the-clock to defend peace on
data.text:
With nearly 40 F-16 Fighting Falcons assigned to the 8th Operations Group’s 80th and 35th Fighter Squadrons, the Wolf Pack is capable of providing combat airpower round-the-clock to defend peace on the Korean Peninsula and support Indo-Pacific priorities.

Always ready. Always watching. May God have mercy on the Wolf Pack’s prey.
